import { Card, Grid2, Typography } from "@mui/material"

function CrearUsuario() {
  return (
    <Grid2 container>
      <Grid2 item xs={3}>
        <Card>
          <Typography>
            Crear tarea
          </Typography>
        </Card>
      </Grid2>
    </Grid2>
  )
}

export default CrearUsuario
